# Devcontainer build context filter.
# Both .devcontainer/ profiles set context to the repo root. Without this
# file the entire repo (.git, node_modules, .venv, .terraform, etc.) is
# sent to the Docker daemon on every build.
#
# The Dockerfile COPY only needs .devcontainer/config/, so deny everything
# else. If another Dockerfile ever needs the repo root as context, switch
# to a selective-exclude strategy instead.
*
!.devcontainer/config/
